  "detailed_description": "<br><br>\"Curse Errant\" is an RPG game produced by \tく～るシスター  and published by Hanabi games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/8dd1bac775ff7bfcf2918768f4262cd0.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><br>In her quest to learn the ways of chivalry, the red-haired knight Giselle found herself serving under Sharon's princess-to-be, Lana. Together, they will uncover the secrets clouding the lands and learn the true meaning behind their destinies. No curse is too powerful to hinder them, no sword is too sharp to cut them down. This is the story of the Curse-Errant Knight.<br><br>This game is a role-playing game featuring a turn-based combat system. It is characterized by a rich and immersive storyline, excellent visual effects and atmospheric music. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/fcf2f92e04e07de3d345ad8c6d452f65.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/ec6ac8d0d4d756252f100e224737a2cc.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=380 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/61f5e3e4cebd55e70bcfeb0d93843c31.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=380 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/909e374333f0de57c8b48f8f3526b2da.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turn-based RPG Combat with an TP Management Feature<br></li><li>Exploration<br></li><li>Side Quests<br></li><li>Events</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br>\"Curse Errant\" is an RPG game produced by \tく～るシスター  and published by Hanabi games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/8dd1bac775ff7bfcf2918768f4262cd0.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><br>In her quest to learn the ways of chivalry, the red-haired knight Giselle found herself serving under Sharon's princess-to-be, Lana. Together, they will uncover the secrets clouding the lands and learn the true meaning behind their destinies. No curse is too powerful to hinder them, no sword is too sharp to cut them down. This is the story of the Curse-Errant Knight.<br><br>This game is a role-playing game featuring a turn-based combat system. It is characterized by a rich and immersive storyline, excellent visual effects and atmospheric music. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/fcf2f92e04e07de3d345ad8c6d452f65.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/ec6ac8d0d4d756252f100e224737a2cc.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=380 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/61f5e3e4cebd55e70bcfeb0d93843c31.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=380 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719250/extras/909e374333f0de57c8b48f8f3526b2da.avif?t=1738628934\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turn-based RPG Combat with an TP Management Feature<br></li><li>Exploration<br></li><li>Side Quests<br></li><li>Events</li></ul>",
